    <p>scAB is publicly available as an R package. Source codes, as well as tutorials have been deposited at the GitHub repository (<ext-link xlink:href="https://github.com/jinworks/scAB" ext-link-type="uri">https://github.com/jinworks/scAB</ext-link>).</p>
